title: NFL ATL: Best receiving corps, OTA roundup with Bucky Brooks
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Best receiving corps, OTA roundup with Bucky Brooks
description:
A room full of heroes -- Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- welcomes Bucky Brooks into Studio 66 to rank the top receiving corps in the NFL and deliver his first-hand observations on OTAs around the league.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
